description:
The city sleeps under a foggy shroud, concealing a night of Crime! Killing, the imperceptible one, targets a royal treasure of a royal treasure of gold coins... but to get it he must run a gauntlet of police, gangsters, seductresses, murderous commie agents and... death!

Notes

As this is a photo-comic the characters are portrayed by live action actors.

Killing is portrayed without credit by Aldo Agliata.

Killing's lover Dana is portrayed by actress Luciana Paoli.

Inspector Mercier is portrayed by actor Dario Michaelis.
